{"tid":113857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京毒霧12秒縮時攝影 網友驚呼：快窒息了！","createTime":"2017-02-09T10:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T10:28:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"663d4fce6964e5fd1d24aae60c479a3ddce027de","tid":113857,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTZS8yc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTZS8yc.jpg&h=3877cef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕毒霧有多可怕？英國工程師波普（Chas Pope）在1日分享一段毒霧襲捲北京的影片，20分鐘濃縮成12秒，畫面驚人讓網友直呼「快窒息了！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-g1zAJS_C2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-g1zAJS_C2k&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8YS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=92079949\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-g1zAJS_C2k</a><br />\n中國北京、天津、河北等鄰近地區在霧霾中迎接2017年，不少民眾在霧濛濛空氣中，於天安門廣場觀賞元旦升旗。<br />\n根據波普1日在推特分享影片，初時畫面中的北京空氣還算乾淨，隨後毒霧從遠方出現，黃褐色的空氣快速直撲而來，畫面相當驚人。波普推文說，當時北京空氣品質指數（AQI）達400以上。<br />\n不少中國網友被這短短12秒影片嚇到，驚呼「這是沙塵暴嗎？」、「看得我的肺不由得一震」、「隔著螢幕都感覺快窒息了」，直說這不是末日嗎？一百年後，長江以北全變沙漠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1936345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1936345&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8YS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b410986a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1936345&h=648f29bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1936345</a>"},{"pid":"e5babb36b47a0f82d3a515b59895a7a72de203e5","tid":113857,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"畫面令我諗起風之谷"},{"pid":"68d2445154027fc26df075f92d19828f72e700d6","tid":113857,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畫面令我諗起風之谷</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ab699625b4660909a151e39beebe0260e51bf5","tid":113857,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畫面令我諗起風之谷</blockquote><br />\n似吖, 瘴氣森林, 周圍都係蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e2ff2d556b8bd593af8f4a750437a52fe014d6","tid":113857,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"回帶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}